thread.title: Ryan
thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by Ryan

author: Ryan
title: Ryan
text:
The quality of the stamp is exactly what I was hoping for, the stamp came very quickly, and the online stamp creator was very easy to use. The only feature I wish was available on the website is the ability to draw and add lines to my stamp. I just created an imagine file with the lines located where I wanted them and uploaded it but someone who is not as familiar with computers might have had a more difficult time.
I will buy from this website again.
